name: Cheeks
description:
Collab w/ Inanç Kutal. Animated artwork + poem.

"Huge Silence
It rumbles for infinite moments
In my skull

I close the curtain
Facing the exhausted eyes
of a taciturn audience

The notion of Time chews my face
To improvise - To perform - To die

Each glimpse of this amphitheater
Is making fun of me"
